rComments: Most dedicated and caring professor I've ever met. Spent hours doing review sessions out of the goodness of his heart, and helped me for hours after lecture when I wasn't even enrolled in his section. Also explains the material very well, at a bit of a fast pace.

An amazing prof that put in tremendous effort to teach the class. He gave many real-life examples to show relevance of course concepts, explained topics incredibly well and was eager to help students understand confusing concepts. His frequent encouragement made the stress of 1st-year much more manageable. I hope to be in his class again someday
